node.text:
I know times have been hard for many fans who have been impacted by the pandemic. That's why it means a lot to me to partner with @instacart and @thenbpa to deliver a few wins to the LA community. We delivered fresh groceries to 3 different families and surprised them with an additional $5000 in Instacart credit!

With Instacart, you can get your groceries safely delivered to your door. Use the offer code AlexCaruso4 for $20 off your first $50+ order*! #GivefromtheCart #InstacartPartner

*Offer valid until 2/7/21, while supplies last. Fees, taxes, and/or tips may apply. Delivery subject to availability, additional terms apply.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Alex Caruso on August 06, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'wish SHOPPING AKERS 4'.

node.text:
Where to begin.. the past 4 years in LA have been nothing short of special. Allowing an undrafted kid from College Station, Texas to create a career playing basketball in the NBA. Thank you to the SBL and LAL front offices, all my SBL and LAL coaches, and all my teammates for believing in me and allowing me to be myself. I’ve been privileged to call this prestigious franchise my home and I’ll forever be grateful. Lastly, to the fans, THANK YOU! from the jump y’all appreciated my effort and love for the game ..I’m glad I could repay y’all with helping this franchise hoist another banner. We’re connected for life 💛💜
From relatively unknown summer league player ..to an NBA CHAMP.. to another NBA contract.. A new chapter begins

node.text: Always the best workout on @tonal! I love how it tracks every rep you do so you can see your progress in real time. With its advanced technology and dynamic weight modes you can lift with settings like CHAINS, ECCENTRIC, SMART FLEX and BURN OUT which make every rep I do count to the fullest. Check out their IG to learn more. #BeYourStrongest #TeamTonal
